g.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2816454235257316&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=cbf666f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2816454235257316</a><br />\n<br />\n舅父到底去咗邊？點解一開始係舅父求助？點解坐監嘅「男朋友證人」會話陳小朋友討厭舅父？點解「朋友證人」一律話陳小朋友會周圍同人傾家事？係唔係典型嘅盤問植入假記憶？係嘅話點解要玩呢招？邊個中招？邊個惡意偽證？唔係嘅話舅父係咪兇手，超級煙幕高人？<br />\n<br />\n又唔係冇舅父喎，因為同「討厭舅父」矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n「入過青山嘅老豆」又去咗邊？唔使傳召？"},{"pid":"492da33fcbc732233376e8d057992f9cc74c3d59","tid":2178212,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c56f7428e7e1a7c016c27c157703b782b6e608","tid":2178212,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1b1469435c93666c9cc8036b86945a04e291856c","tid":2178212,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d97a2cb3716bd5d8767cf19b487e5b0d44889e1","tid":2178212,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:27:09.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d2286283ded4ad59d26ba9affb3a5c7c37321b","tid":2178212,"uid":51033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"黃屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c9d6c6793769906f4637bf393bcab7ff8e35d7","tid":2178212,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20